Package cmu.ds.mr.mapred

Interface Summary
Mapper<K1,V1,K2,V2> The mapper class of MapReduce framework
Reducer<K1,V1,K2,V2> The reducer class of the MapReduce framework
RunningJob Adapted and changed from Hadoop.
 

Class Summary
Job Job class for running job
JobClient JobClient is used to submit jobs from local to jobtracker
JobID JobID is used to privide the identifier for job
JobInProgress JobInProgress is used to record running jobs with its status and config on JobTracker
JobManager JobManager is used to check and kill running jobs on JobTracker
JobStatus JobStatus is used to record jobs' status which is used to identify and check the specified job
JobTracker JobTracker is used to control all TaskTrackers All jobs are submitted to jobtracker and then assigned to all other tasktrackers
MapReduceBase Base class for Mapper and Reducer.
MapTask MapTask: the map task class to run the mapper class
ReduceTask ReduceTask: the reduce task class to run the reduce class
Task The abstract class for Task
TaskID Task ID class: An example TaskID is : task_200707121733_0003_m_000005_01 , which represents the first try of fifth map task in the third job running at the jobtracker started at 200707121733.
TaskRunner Class for running mappaer and reducer in a separate thread
TaskStatus Task status to keep track of task progress and state
TaskTracker TaskTracker: the class for launch, kill tasks and heartbeating with jobTracker
TaskTrackerStatus TaskTrackerStatus class used to communication between TaskTracker and JobTracker for all task status in current taskTracker
TimeoutController
